{
  "$schema": "https://github.com/pretinhuu1-boop/blindar/blob/main/schemas/module-map.schema.json",
  "version": "0.45.0",
  "description": "Mapa estruturado dos 18 módulos do launcher → agentes ativados → fases onde rodam. Consumido pelas Fases 02 (discovery), 04 (rounds-loop) e 06 (production-checklist) pra filtrar agentes pelo array config.selected_modules. v0.45: +graph-builder (m1), +módulo 18 (smoke/runtime truth + homolog-only).",
  "modules": {
    "1": {
      "name": "Baseline & Discovery",
      "mandatory": true,
      "skip_token": "always-on",
      "agents": [
        "graph-builder",
        "strategic-scanner"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "00-strategic-scan",
        "01-baseline",
        "02-discovery"
      ]
    },
    "2": {
      "name": "Segurança aplicacional core + AI/LLM + Tenant isolation + File uploads + MLOps",
      "mandatory": true,
      "skip_token": "core-security",
      "agents": [
        "access-control",
        "cryptography",
        "business-logic",
        "runtime-secrets",
        "security",
        "auth-premium",
        "ai-llm-safety",
        "prompt-injection-defense",
        "mcp-security",
        "rag-quality",
        "vector-db-security",
        "fine-tune-data-leak",
        "tenant-isolation-tests",
        "file-uploads",
        "mlops",
        "prototype-pollution",
        "llm-system-prompt-leak",
        "semgrep",
        "gitleaks"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop",
        "05-adversarial-review"
      ]
    },
    "3": {
      "name": "Frontend hardening (CSP/XSS/SRI/Trusted Types)",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "ui_detected"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "frontend",
        "client-open-redirect"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop"
      ]
    },
    "4": {
      "name": "Rede & API + Payments + Realtime + API Gateway + GraphQL + gRPC",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "project_type:saas",
        "project_type:ecom",
        "project_type:api"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "network-security",
        "api-design",
        "payments",
        "realtime",
        "api-gateway",
        "graphql",
        "grpc-internal",
        "api-surface-isolation"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop"
      ]
    },
    "5": {
      "name": "Supply chain & patch + SBOM/SLSA (compliance 2026)",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "always"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "supply-chain",
        "patch-management",
        "sbom-slsa",
        "osv-scanner",
        "trivy"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop"
      ]
    },
    "6": {
      "name": "Observabilidade & audit + Cost monitoring",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "project_type:saas",
        "project_type:ecom",
        "project_type:api"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "observability",
        "cost-observability"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop"
      ]
    },
    "7": {
      "name": "Banco de dados + Backup & DR + Multi-region + Data Warehouse/ETL",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "db_detected"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "backup-recovery",
        "db-architect",
        "multi-region",
        "data-warehouse-etl"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop",
        "06-production-checklist"
      ]
    },
    "8": {
      "name": "Compliance: LGPD + GDPR + HIPAA + PCI-DSS + frameworks",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "data_sensitivity:high",
        "data_sensitivity:medium",
        "rigor:compliance"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "compliance-lgpd-br",
        "compliance",
        "compliance-gdpr",
        "compliance-hipaa",
        "compliance-pci-deep",
        "fintech-banking-br",
        "healthtech-fhir",
        "ecom-checkout-conversion",
        "regulatory-mapper"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop",
        "06-production-checklist"
      ]
    },
    "9": {
      "name": "Performance backend + Query + CDN strategy",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "project_type:saas",
        "project_type:ecom",
        "project_type:api"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "performance",
        "db-architect",
        "cdn-strategy",
        "redis-patterns"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop"
      ]
    },
    "10": {
      "name": "Fluidez completa + SEO + Frontend gen + Search + Push + Mobile native + Analytics + Audio + Video",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "ui_detected"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "frontend-performance",
        "responsive-a11y",
        "govtech-acessibilidade",
        "pwa-installable",
        "i18n-tz",
        "state-cache-data",
        "onboarding-ux",
        "seo-marketing-meta",
        "frontend-generator",
        "search-quality",
        "push-notifications",
        "mobile-native",
        "embedded-analytics",
        "audio-voice",
        "video-streaming",
        "session-timeout-ux"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop",
        "06-production-checklist"
      ]
    },
    "11": {
      "name": "Funcional E2E + Testing strategy + Visual regression",
      "mandatory": true,
      "skip_token": "no-mock-no-broken",
      "agents": [
        "functional-e2e",
        "testing-strategy",
        "visual-regression"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop",
        "06-production-checklist"
      ]
    },
    "12": {
      "name": "Anti-mock + Externalização + Content quality (gramática/tom/glossário)",
      "mandatory": true,
      "skip_token": "no-mock-no-broken",
      "agents": [
        "mock-killer",
        "config-externalization",
        "content-quality"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop",
        "06-production-checklist"
      ]
    },
    "13": {
      "name": "Resiliência + escalabilidade + Process + Scheduled jobs + Chaos + Event-driven",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "rigor:production",
        "rigor:compliance"
      ],
      "default_off_when": [
        "rigor:mvp"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "resilience",
        "scalability",
        "process-resilience",
        "scheduled-jobs",
        "chaos-engineering",
        "event-driven",
        "queue-management",
        "fallback-resilience"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop"
      ]
    },
    "14": {
      "name": "DX + Flags + Backoffice + Email + Docs + Reports + Architect + Delivery + Project bootstrap (scaffold do zero)",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [
        "always"
      ],
      "agents": [
        "devops",
        "feature-flags",
        "backoffice-admin",
        "email-deliverability",
        "documentation-live",
        "execution-report",
        "architect",
        "delivery-bundle",
        "project-bootstrap",
        "mcp-recommender",
        "blindar-fix",
        "solution-architect"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "03-bootstrap-sec-html",
        "04-rounds-loop",
        "06-production-checklist",
        "07-final-report"
      ]
    },
    "15": {
      "name": "Pentest + adversarial review",
      "mandatory": true,
      "skip_token": "always-on",
      "agents": [
        "pentest",
        "adversarial-reviewer",
        "wave-guardian",
        "proactive-analysis"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "05-adversarial-review",
        "06-production-checklist"
      ]
    },
    "16": {
      "name": "Product Evolution (opt-in, escopo separado do hardening)",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [],
      "skip_token": "evolution-only",
      "agents": [
        "api-frontend-coverage",
        "user-journey-simulator",
        "feature-gap-analyzer",
        "growth-opportunities",
        "product-critic"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "07-evolution"
      ],
      "entrypoint": "scripts/blindar-evolve.sh",
      "notes": "Roda separado via scripts/blindar-evolve.sh. NUNCA entra no --fast. Requer ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (todos agentes API-wrapped)."
    },
    "17": {
      "name": "blindar ataque — recon passivo externo (URL)",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [],
      "skip_token": "attack-recon-only",
      "agents": [
        "attack-recon"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "09-attack-recon"
      ],
      "entrypoint": "scripts/attack-recon.sh",
      "notes": "Modo PASSIVO puro (só GET/HEAD/OPTIONS, rate 1/3s, UA browser). Zero payload de ataque → não dispara WAF, seguro pra produção. Opt-in via roles:[attack-recon] ou --attack. Precisa da URL como arg."
    },
    "18": {
      "name": "Smoke / Runtime Truth — prova que a app SOBE + checks de infra/runtime (homolog, nunca dev)",
      "mandatory": true,
      "skip_token": "always-on",
      "agents": [
        "smoke-runtime",
        "homolog-only",
        "deps-sync",
        "worker-jobs",
        "datetime-tz",
        "entrypoint-cmd",
        "alembic-health",
        "notnull-no-default",
        "ratelimit-response",
        "infra-windows"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "04-rounds-loop",
        "06-production-checklist"
      ],
      "entrypoint": "scripts/smoke-run.sh",
      "notes": "Sobe o stack em homolog (mock direto no banco, espelho de produção), espera /health, roda 1 fluxo crítico, flag boot-quebrado e 500 de runtime. self-skips se não há Dockerfile/compose nem --url. Roda DEPOIS de implementar e ANTES do ataque (módulo 15) — provar que sobe é pré-requisito. check-homolog-only proíbe config de dev no artefato."
    },
    "19": {
      "name": "Pentest ATIVO (autorizado) — payloads reais contra alvo autorizado",
      "mandatory": false,
      "default_on_when": [],
      "skip_token": "pentest-active-only",
      "agents": [
        "pentest-active"
      ],
      "phases": [
        "05-adversarial-review"
      ],
      "entrypoint": "scripts/pentest-active.sh",
      "notes": "OPT-IN e GATED: exige .accept-authorization (escopo + 'authorized: yes'). Sem isso RECUSA (zero payloads). Não-destrutivo, rate-limited, escopo-limitado. Uso legítimo: seus produtos ou com autorização. Roda no passo 'atacar' da ordem security-first, depois do smoke."
    }
  },
  "resolution_rules": {
    "description": "Como resolver defaults quando user escolhe 'defaults' no menu. Aplicar em ordem.",
    "rules": [
      "Módulos com mandatory:true sempre entram, independente de tudo",
      "Default ON se default_on_when contém 'always'",
      "Default ON se default_on_when contém condição que bate (ui_detected, db_detected, project_type:X, data_sensitivity:Y, rigor:Z)",
      "Default OFF se default_off_when contém condição que bate (sobrescreve ON)",
      "Resto fica OFF até user incluir manualmente"
    ]
  },
  "consumer_contract": {
    "description": "Como pipeline consome este arquivo. Ler ANTES de spawnar agentes em qualquer fase.",
    "steps": [
      "Ler .blindar/config.yml do projeto-alvo",
      "Para cada agente que a fase atual quer rodar, verificar: módulo do agente está em config.selected_modules?",
      "Se SIM: spawn agente normalmente",
      "Se NÃO: pular (log: 'agent X skipped: module Y not in selected_modules')",
      "Se selected_modules estiver vazio/missing: rodar todos (compat com v0.7 e abaixo)"
    ]
  }
}
